\begin_layout Standard

\emph on
Luminous: the Dream
\emph default
 is a game about those who dream of a better future inspired by the 
\shape italic
mahou shoujo
\shape default
 (or magical girl) genre of Japanese anime and manga.
 It is set in the Chronicles of Darkness, a world much like our own only
 touched by alien wonders and terrors alike.
 This story is not truly about those horrors.
 It is about humanity, and the one power we can truly call our own.
 Our shining will to change the world.
 A will that blossomed into a force that could only be called magic.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
In this game, you play a Luminous, one of the shining souls that wields
 the power of the Dream.
 Those like you were hidden, shining dimly through so much of history.
 ...
 but shine they did.
 Writing into the untold margins of history, they built the legacy you now
 inherent.
 When you Blossomed, you awoke to the world of dreams they hid deep beyond
 the veil of sleep.
 Drawing on that grand Dream, you found a magic you just maybe could truly
 change the world with.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
It will not be easy.
 The world has always been an unkind place.
 Generations of darkness scar the heart of humanity.
 So many people are afraid to dream, and so focus on preserving what they
 already have.
 So many people are scared that any change to the world would crumble it
 all down, and hence fear those who dream brightly.
 Some people once dreamed, and had them broken by those who were scared
 in just the same way.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Glimmers of light shine through that long and dark night.
 We had created so many wonders over the generations, and they simply accumulate.
