\begin_layout Subsection*
Senki Zesshou Symphogear
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
While more seinen than most conventional magical girl shows, Symphogear
 is underlined with themes of heartfelt communication between people who
 otherwise misunderstand each other, determination to protect, and what
 we sacrifice in order to protect.
 The main character, Hibiki, embodies much of what the Luminous stand for,
 with her belief in the ability to reach to the heart, and the refusal to
 give up in the heart of darkness, whether it be in actual battle or peoples
 own despair.
 Each member of the main cast suffers tragedy, and it’s through their bonds
 with others that they’re able to stand up again.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection*
The Lego Movie 2: The Second Part
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Whereas the first movie focused on creativity and freedom, the second discusses
