\end_inset

 Attributes are the innate characteristics of your character, such as how
 fast, charismatic or smart she is.
 When choosing your attributes, ask yourself what would lead your character
 to lead to her living the life she does, what she would choose to develop,
 what skills she relies on, and whether she uses her magic or mundane skills
 to achieve her goals.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Luminous and characters who are intended to Blossom in play do not choose
 their attributes like most characters.
 Begin by assign dots to her three 
