 Begin with 1 dot in each dream attribute, then assign 8 dots between then,
 up to a maximum of 6 dots in any attribute.
 Then, beginning with 1 dot in each mundane attribute, distribute 12 dots
 between your character's mundane attributes up to a maximum of 5 dots in
 any attribute.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
None of your character's mundane attributes may exceed their corresponding
 dream attribute and you may not assign more than 5 dots to each of the
 mundane attribute categories (Physical, Mental and Social).
 If the highest mundane attribute corresponding to a dream attribute is
 lower than the amount you assigned earlier, gain the remainder as dream
 attribute dots.
\end_layout

