, and choose the one that fits your character concept the best.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
It may well be that your character could fit into multiple Luminaries.
 Often, such characters tend to have the Luminary that reflects the kind
 of power they would be more comfortable wielding, if their personality
 could go either way.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsubsection*
Archetype 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Whether your character would be a shining hero, an idol whose songs change
 the world, or a shrine maiden that upholds the boundary between worlds,
 she is yet still a Luminous.
 The Luminous have taken on many forms and roles over their long history,
 after all.
 Her Archetype reflects which of those legacies she would wish to continue
