 Read over the Kingdoms and choose the one that your character would most
 believe in.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsubsection*
Dream & Will
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Choose your character's Dream and Will.
 While most mortals have a Virtue and a Vice, Luminous draw their strength
 from their dearest dreams and shining will.
 Her Dream is the ideal world she would wish to live in, far in the distant
 future.
 It is the hope she clings to when she needs reminding what she is fighting
 for, and the world she dreams of in her sleep.
 Her Will is the means by which she changes the world, and interacts with
 it.
 It is the part of herself she draws on to face the challenges the world
 bring against her, how she connects with a world that seems far too foreign
