\begin_inset Quotes xrd
\end_inset

, while one who supports her family and friends may have a Will of 
\begin_inset Quotes xld
\end_inset

Counceler
\begin_inset Quotes xrd
\end_inset

.
 Whenever a Luminous overcomes a challenge in affirming her Will, she regains
 one Willpower.
 Whenever a Luminous takes a significant risk in the process, she regains
 all Willpower.
\end_layout

