 her Resistance + transformed attribute cap.
 It serves as her health track for all purposes in Dream Form.
 She may transform reflexively in response to damage, in which case the
 damage is dealt to her Dream Health.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Dream Health is more her will to not be hurt manifest physically than a
